title: Airbus - worldwide aircraft deliveries 2002 to 2019
summary: In general Number of aircraft deliveries has rose over the Year.
Number of aircraft deliveries is roughly constant from 2003 to 2004, slightly increasing from 2004 to 2006, and finally roughly constant from 2006 to 2009.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2004 and 2005.
Maximum Number of aircraft deliveries, about 498.0 was reported at Year 2009
Minimum Number of aircraft deliveries about 305.0 was reached at Year 2003
